creator: Local Express
descriptionHtml:
Los Gatos Meats and Smokehouse is not only a local staple, but also a piece of our town’s history. Established in 1891, generations of families worked to maintain this business’ legacy, passing on new traditions for generations to come. Here at Los Gatos Meats, we feature high quality, specialty meats cut to order, delicious deli sandwiches, house-made marinades & products, and custom processing. Being family owned and operated in this location since 1991, we provide warm, friendly service that truly makes you feel connected to our community.
Los Gatos Meats is open and is here to serve the community. We are trying to find a balance of serving the community and keeping our customers satisfied. Los Gatos Meats appreciates the support of our customers.
